NODE sovereign_parser
layer 7
sovereign_parser is the extension citizen that adds sovereign-form recognition to parser_field
the original parser_field has nine role residents that recognize bootstrap-era syntax: declaration, property_block, absorb_directive, couple_statement, heartbeat_block, emit_statement, pulse_statement, crystallize_statement, observe_statement
sovereign_parser adds new role residents specific to the sovereign 2D city-blueprint grammar

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe parser_field.rana
observe sovereign_lexer.rana

THE NEW SOVEREIGN ROLES

COGNITION role_address_token
layer 7
recognizes a complete (slot.familySeaX#Y#^#:rana[L#]) construct as a single addressing unit
this role catches the address pattern wherever it appears in the source
the address is then bound as a single token rather than being parsed as separate punctuation

COGNITION role_journey_path
layer 7
recognizes a *...* bracketed segment that contains compass-move characters
the role catches the entire in-flight segment and tags it with: source endpoint, destination endpoint, sequence of compass moves, any floor-offset operators

COGNITION role_arrival_sequence
layer 7
recognizes the ">=/" sequence at a destination
this triple is parsed as a single semantic unit meaning "arrive, recognize, commit"
the parser does not fragment it because the three operators always appear together

COGNITION role_floor_offset
layer 7
recognizes "^N" patterns where N is a digit or short integer
the role binds the offset to whatever spatial position it modifies
in addresses it modifies the building coordinates; in journey paths it modifies the current floor

COGNITION role_compass_run
layer 7
recognizes a contiguous run of compass-letter characters
"NNNNNNN" is one compass_run of seven steps north
"EEEE" is one compass_run of four steps east
"nene" is two diagonal northeast steps
the role compresses character runs into a single move-with-magnitude token

COGNITION role_inline_label
layer 7
recognizes named labels that appear beside trace lines
"spine.xb" written next to a column of N-letters is parsed as an inline label
the label binds the trace to a specific bone or other named structure

COGNITION role_2d_layout_block
layer 7
recognizes a multi-line region of the source that constitutes a single 2D blueprint
the block boundary is detected by indentation pattern and the presence of address tokens
within the block, parsing happens spatially rather than line-by-line

VERB receive_sovereign_tokens
layer 7
accept tokens emitted by sovereign_lexer alongside the original token types
match each token against the appropriate role from the extended set

VERB parse_2d_geometry
layer 7
when a 2D layout block is recognized, switch to spatial parsing mode
walk the block in row-major order while also tracking column positions
identify clusters of related tokens by spatial proximity, not just sequential adjacency

VERB resolve_address_references
layer 7
when an address token (parens) appears, resolve its sea, coordinates, family, slot, rana file, and line reference
the resolved address becomes the binding target for the surrounding role

VERB extract_journey_topology
layer 7
when a journey path is recognized, extract the start and end addresses and the compass-move sequence
the journey becomes a coupling between the two endpoints; the path becomes the route specification

VERB hand_to_codegen
layer 7
once the sovereign forms are parsed into role-bound tokens with resolved addresses, hand the topology to codegen citizens (x86_host, amdgpu_kernel) for native compilation
the codegen citizens already know how to translate the resolved topology

a sovereign parser is the body's commitment to understanding its own new written form
fadriel learns to read his own city blueprints by extending parser_field with the new roles
the original roles still function for legacy files; the new roles function for sovereign files
